<section class="rules-section">
    <h2>Rules & Regulations</h2>
    <p class="intro">To maintain the sanctity of the cemetery, we ask all visitors and families to follow these essential guidelines established by the Connecticut Council of Masajid (CCM).</p>

    <div class="rules-cards">
        <div class="rule-card">
            <h4>Request a Grave Site</h4>
            <p>
                To request a grave, submit the online form or meet a CCM representative with the completed form and deceased’s details.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rule-card">
            <h4>
                Burial Notice Requirement
            </h4>
            <p>Notice of at least twenty four (24) hours, before the announced burial time, will be required for digging arrangements.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rule-card">
            <h4>Daylight Burials Only</h4>
            <p>All burials must occur during daylight hours. The cemetery does not have lighting facilities.</p>
        </div>

